# Test Cases

## TC001 – User Registration
| Field | Value |
|-------|--------|
| Objective | Validate new user registration |
| Precondition | User not registered |
| Steps | 1. Navigate to Registration page 2. Enter valid details 3. Submit |
| Expected | User account created |

## TC002 – Login with valid credentials
Objective: Validate login  
Steps: Enter valid username/password  
Expected: User lands on My Account

## TC003 – Search Product
Steps: Enter "iPhone" in search bar  
Expected: Relevant products displayed

## TC004 – Add to Cart
Steps: Open product → Add to Cart  
Expected: Product added successfully

## TC005 – Checkout
Steps: Cart → Checkout → Enter details → Confirm  
Expected: Order placed
